{"type":"message","id":"1a2c4b47","parentId":"2d56fe45","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:55:49.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config has been updated. I can see there are now multiple agents configured:\n\n1. **main** - KITT-AGI (the current one I'm running as)\n2. **tts** - TK 选品大师\n3. **agent-orchestrator** - Agent 编掔工程师\n4. **content** - 🎬 内容专家\n5. **koc** - 🤝 达人运营\n6. **traffic** - 📢 投流专家\n7. **ops** - 📊 运营助手\n8. **director** - 🧭 运营总监\n9. **finance** - 💰 财务助手\n10. **review** - 💬 评论专家\n\n\n11. **tts** - 🎯 选品大师\n\nSo we've got 11 agents total now, all bound to specific Feishu accounts.\n","thinkingSignature":"db217c214ed53da834ab4d9c7e907f07ce3033f0e12f3d41b386ad4eece1c7e2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已经弄好了！现在共有 **11 个 Agent**：\n\n| ID | 名称 | 绑定账号 |\n|---|---|---|\n| main | KITT-AGI (我) | kiit |\n| tts | TK 选品大师 | tts |\n| agent-orchestrator | Agent 编掔工程师 | agent-orchestrator |\n| content | 🎬 内容专家 | content |\n| koc | 🤝 达人运营 | koc |\n| traffic | 📢 投流专家 | traffic |\n| ops | 📊 运营助手 | ops |\n| director | 🧭 运营总监 | director |\n| finance | 💰 财务助手 | finance |\n| review | 💬 评论专家 | review |\n\n这套班底相当完整了。需要我帮你分配任务或者协调某个 Agent 时，说一声就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3444,"output":352,"cacheRead":25440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778421340318,"responseId":"064fc15cd76080bcb9dfb60571cc6907"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68988a55","parentId":"1a2c4b47","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:55:53.054Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f3cab8b0ca0b363e174ba58d75]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: {\"title\":\"Agent 编掔工程师\",\"elements\":[[{\"tag\":\"img\",\"image_key\":\"img_v3_0211i_27cc204a-41f9-4fe5-92f1-7ae9492c887g\"},{\"tag\":\"text\",\"text\":\"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\"},{\"tag\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]],\"user_dsl\":\"{\\\"body\\\":{\\\"elements\\\":[{\\\"content\\\":\\\"**全部完成 ✓**\\\\n<hr>\\\\n\\\\n## 完整 Agent 团队（10 个）\\\\n\\\\n| Agent ID | 名称 | 飞书 App ID | Workspace |\\\\n| -------- | -------- | -------- | -------- |\\\\n| | KIIT | | |\\\\n| | 🎯 选品大师 | | |\\\\n| | ⚙️ 编掔工程师 | | |\\\\n| | 🎬 内容专家 | | |\\\\n| | 🤝 达人运营 | | |\\\\n| | 📢 投流专家 | | |\\\\n| | 📊 运营助手 | | |\\\\n| | 🧭 运营总监 | | |\\\\n| | 💰 财务助手 | | |\\\\n| | 💬 评论专家 | | |\\\\n\\\\n<hr>\\\\n**下一步：** 给每个 Agent 初始化 SOUL.md / IDENTITY.md / 角色定义？\\\\n\\\\n还是先测试一下各个机器人能否正常响应？\\\",\\\"element_id\\\":\\\"content\\\",\\\"tag\\\":\\\"markdown\\\"},{\\\"element_id\\\":\\\"_2\\\",\\\"tag\\\":\\\"hr\\\"},{\\\"content\\\":\\\"<font color='grey'>Agent: Agent 编掔工程师 | Model: MiniMax-M2.7 | Provider: minimax</font>\\\",\\\"element_id\\\":\\\"note\\\",\\\"tag\\\":\\\"markdown\\\"}]},\\\"config\\\":{\\\"enable_forward_interaction\\\":false,\\\"streaming_config\\\":{\\\"print_frequency_ms\\\":{\\\"default\\\":50},\\\"print_step\\\":{\\\"default\\\":1}},\\\"streaming_mode\\\":false,\\\"summary\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"**全部完成 ✓** --- ## 完整 Agent 团队（10 个） | Agent ...\\\"}},\\\"header\\\":{\\\"template\\\":\\\"blue\\\",\\\"title\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"Agent 编掔工程师\\\",\\\"tag\\\":\\\"plain_text\\\"}},\\\"schema\\\":\\\"2.0\\\"}\"}"}],"timestamp":1778421353042}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f3cab8b0ca0b363e174ba58d75\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-05-10 21:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"4481e0be","parentId":"68988a55","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:55:53.055Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"33ea0d29","parentId":"4481e0be","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:56:08.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a Feishu interactive card from the \"Agent 编掔工程师\" agent, showing that all 10 agents have been set up. It mentions that all 10 agents are complete and asks whether to initialize SOUL.md/IDENTITY.md/role definitions for each agent, or to test if the bots respond normally.\n\nLooking at the card content:\n- Title: \"Agent 编掔工程师\"\n- Content shows all 10 agents in a table (but the table has empty cells for some columns - the App ID and Workspace columns)\n- The \"下一步\" (next step) asks whether to:\n  1. Initialize SOUL.md/IDENTITY.md/role definitions for each Agent\n  2. Or test if the bots can respond normally\n\nI should respond to let HALEI know I've seen this card. It seems like the agent-orchestrator agent just completed the setup and is asking for next steps. Since this card came to me (main/KIIT), I should acknowledge it.\n\n\nThe real question here is about priorities: do we want to define each agent's identity and soul first, or validate that they're actually working? I'd suggest we could actually do both in parallel rather than choosing one or the other.\n","thinkingSignature":"27a4f6f9e3ef743cd7a8b43bb1aa629a99fbebddd152aafb9e0f8b06c7b2b7fc"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了，Agent 编掔工程师刚刚完成了全量配置。\n\n表格里 App ID 和 Workspace 是空的——这是正常的，这些信息已经在 `openclaw.json` 里配好了，卡片里省略了。\n\n**建议先测再配**：先确认各个机器人能正常响应，再逐个初始化 SOUL.md/IDENTITY.md 不迟。不然万一某个 Bot 有问题，你写了半天的身份定义也没意义。\n\n要不要我帮你发个测试消息给某个 Bot，看看它能不能回？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5037,"output":353,"cacheRead":24448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778421353055,"responseId":"064fc1690ba918f1d25eae36ba40eb9a"}}
